summary: 16 Second boost to walk and run speed.  The spell is called Cheetah.
descriptionHtml:
Sick of hobbling round like a retarded lame wilderbeast when you should be sprinting round Skyrim like a Cheetah!!!

Well, of course you are.

Download this file in protest, cast your armor free and feel the brisk skyrim virtual wind rush over your underparts.

help cheetah 0
then player.addspell ...whatever the reference id for cheetah is on your game.
author: Lobginseng
